## Limitations
The findings are based on available online resources and may not encompass all perspectives on the topic. The search was limited to English-language sources, which may exclude insights from non-English speaking regions. Additionally, the dynamic nature of workplace cultures means that the importance of discussing accomplishments can vary significantly across different industries and organizational structures.